    <p>If you are searching for a spa in Carmel, Indiana, you have more options than a traditional day spa. A full-service salon and spa like Glow Salon &amp; Spa offers everything from nail services and waxing to hair color and makeup — all in one appointment, without needing to visit multiple locations. Here is what to know before you book.</p>

    <h2>What Spa Services Are Available in Carmel, Indiana?</h2>
    <p>Glow Salon &amp; Spa is a full-service salon and spa located in the Village of West Clay in Carmel, Indiana. Our services span several categories, so you can address more than one thing in a single visit.</p>

    <p>Our <a href="/services/nails">nail services</a> include spa pedicures, gel manicures, dip powder, and classic manicures. For <a href="/services/hair">hair</a>, we offer cuts, blowouts, balayage, highlights, all-over color, keratin treatments, and extensions. Our waxing menu covers brow shaping and lip waxing, and our <a href="/services/makeup">makeup</a> services include both touch-up appointments and full glam looks for events. We also offer <a href="/services">bridal hair and makeup</a> packages for wedding parties.</p>

    <p>If you are not sure where to start, our team is happy to walk you through what would make the most sense for your goals and budget during a consultation at your appointment.</p>

    <h2>What to Expect During Your First Spa Visit</h2>
    <p>First-time clients often wonder what the experience will look like. At Glow Salon &amp; Spa, we keep things straightforward and comfortable. There is no complicated check-in process or pressure to purchase add-ons you did not ask for.</p>

    <p>A few things that make your visit go smoothly: plan to arrive five to ten minutes before your appointment time. This gives you a moment to settle in, review the menu if you have questions, and let your service provider know about any preferences or sensitivities before you start. If you are getting a color service, bring a few inspiration photos — they are genuinely useful and help your stylist understand the result you are imagining, not just the name of a shade.</p>

    <p>Do not hesitate to ask about products used during your service. Our team is happy to explain what they are applying and why, and to recommend at-home care that will extend the results of your appointment.</p>

    <h2>Most Popular Spa Services in Carmel</h2>
